'''Ampere''' (calaamad: '''[[Ampere|A]]'''), oo inta badan lagu soo gaabiyo amp, waa unugga hadda korantada ee [[Nidaamka Caalamiga ah ee Unugyada]] (SI).  Hal ampere waxa ay la mid tahay 6.241509074×10<sup>18</sup> elegteroon qiimihiisu waxa uu dhaafayaa dhibic ilbiriqsi gudaheed.

Waxaa loo magacaabay ka dib markii xisaabyahan Faransiis ah iyo fisiigis [[André-Marie Ampère]] (1775-1836), loo arkaa aabbihiis elegteromagneetism oo uu weheliyo physicist Danish Hans Christian Ørsted.
